**File**: `/home/openclaw/code/tuicraft/src/wow/client.ts` (lines 150-194)

The `WorldHandle` is the public API:

```typescript
export type WorldHandle = {
  closed: Promise<void>;
  close(): void;
  onMessage(cb: (msg: ChatMessage) => void): void;

  // Existing methods for groups:
  invite(name: string): void;
  uninvite(name: string): void;
  leaveGroup(): void;
  setLeader(name: string): void;
  acceptInvite(): void;
  declineInvite(): void;
  onGroupEvent(cb: (event: GroupEvent) => void): void;

  // Existing methods for friends:
  getFriends(): FriendEntry[];
  addFriend(name: string): void;
  removeFriend(name: string): void;
  onFriendEvent(cb: (event: FriendEvent) => void): void;

  // Guild methods would be added here
