CMSG_GUILD_ROSTER: 0x089,  // ← Request roster
SMSG_GUILD_ROSTER: 0x08a,  // ← Receive roster
CMSG_GUILD_PROMOTE: 0x08b,
CMSG_GUILD_DEMOTE: 0x08c,
CMSG_GUILD_LEAVE: 0x08d,
CMSG_GUILD_REMOVE: 0x08e,
// ... more guild opcodes
```

